of Che tribe and was on September 12, 1981, duly adopted/rejected by

a vote of 19 for, and 5 against, in an election in which at

least thirty percent (30%) of the 57 entitled to vote cast their 

ballots in accordance with Section 16 of the Indian Reorganization Act 

of June 18, 1934 (48 Stat. 984), as amended by the Act of June 15, 1935

(49 Stat. 378).

